{"tid":2000538,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共匪：倡食肆放寬每枱至6人 母親節救助紅色經濟圈","createTime":"2020-05-04T02:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T02:46:26.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3455412203fce7ce0afb7c91812f56412e3303","tid":2000538,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:36:14.000Z","msg":"黃家和相信食肆每枱人數一定會放寬至6人<br />\n04.05.2020 10:00<br />\n<br />\n香港餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和在本台節目指，業界一直有與政府就放寬限制措施溝通，聽政府口吻，他相信食肆每枱人數一定會放寬至6人，但會否再進一步放寬，有待明天行政會議拍板。他表示，不少酒樓有接到母親節6至8人套餐的預訂，指母親節是業界最賺錢其中一個節日，以往都有3.5億至4億生意額，期望放寬措施後，有助業界生意回升。<br />\n<br />\n另外，黃家和在一個電台節目表示，業界會配合政府做足防疫措施，酒樓亦願意將每枱之間距離加至1.8米。他又指，酒吧有戶外位置，應該可以解除部分的營業禁令，讓酒吧在有條件和空間下重開，但卡拉OK在室內地方，傳播風險較高，有待當局決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285002&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1285002%26csid%3D261_341&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXyfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=d697eccc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285002&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"53bd15ecc98d19564bebcdc1706246137033ed81","tid":2000538,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"OK，搞完五一去搞母親節 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dac01f32ec182a89abf961fd01d75ad98fa0837","tid":2000538,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/95178781_142036260714480_6480402155495751680_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=ae9BbWjHZxoAX84xvYm&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=222f198c2fe1bc1166d03303f637a68a&amp;oe=5ED4DF0E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F95178781_142036260714480_6480402155495751680_o.jpg%3F_nc_ca